                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>Dear Harmony Community,</p>
                    
                    <p>We're writing to inform you that the Harmony mobile application has been discontinued effective immediately. After extensive evaluation, we've determined that the mobile app could not meet our quality standards due to persistent technical challenges.</p>
                    
                    <p>We're excited to share that our <span class="highlight">web platform remains fully operational</span> and offers a significantly improved experience with minimal technical issues.</p>
                    
                    <div class="warning">
                        <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i>
                        <div>
                            <strong>Important Notice:</strong> Due to technical limitations, your mobile app data (playlists, favorites) cannot be transferred to the web platform. You'll need to start fresh on the web version.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <p>The Harmony web application is now the primary way to access our service, offering:</p>
                    
                    <div class="features-grid">
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt feature-icon"></i>
                            <h3 class="feature-title">Mobile Optimized</h3>
                            <p class="feature-desc">Fully responsive design for all smartphones and tablets</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <i class="fas fa-bolt feature-icon"></i>
                            <h3 class="feature-title">Enhanced Performance</h3>
                            <p class="feature-desc">Faster loading and smoother streaming experience</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <i class="fas fa-sync-alt feature-icon"></i>
                            <h3 class="feature-title">Instant Updates</h3>
