        <!-- Info Tab -->
        <section id="info" class="tab-content">
            <div class="page-header">
                <div>
                    <h1 class="page-title">Mobile App Technical Issues</h1>
                    <p class="page-subtitle">Understanding what went wrong with Harmony mobile</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="content-card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <div class="card-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-bug"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="card-title">Technical Challenges</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>Developing and maintaining the Harmony mobile application presented several significant technical challenges that ultimately led to our decision to discontinue the app:</p>
                    
                    <div class="features-grid">
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle feature-icon"></i>
                            <h3 class="feature-title">Platform Fragmentation</h3>
                            <p class="feature-desc">Incompatibilities across thousands of Android/iOS versions and devices</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <i class="fas fa-battery-quarter feature-icon"></i>
                            <h3 class="feature-title">Resource Consumption</h3>
                            <p class="feature-desc">Excessive battery drain and memory usage issues</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <i class="fas fa-sync feature-icon"></i>
                            <h3 class="feature-title">Update Delays</h3>
                            <p class="feature-desc">App store review processes prevented timely bug fixes</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <i class="fas fa-database feature-icon"></i>
                            <h3 class="feature-title">Data Syncing Issues</h3>
                            <p class="feature-desc">Inability to reliably sync data with web platform</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <p>After months of attempting to resolve these issues, we determined that the resources required to maintain an acceptable mobile experience would be better invested in improving our web platform, which doesn't suffer from these limitations.</p>
                    
                    <div class="warning">
                        <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i>
                        <div>
                            <strong>Data Transfer Notice:</strong> Due to the technical issues with our mobile infrastructure, we are unable to transfer your mobile app data to the web platform. We sincerely apologize for this inconvenience.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="content-card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <div class="card-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="card-title">Our Path Forward</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>By focusing exclusively on our web platform, we can:</p>
                    
                    <ul style="padding-left: 30px; margin: 25px 0; line-height: 2;">
                        <li>Deliver new features more rapidly</li>
                        <li>Ensure a consistent experience across all devices</li>
                        <li>Reduce maintenance overhead</li>
                        <li>Focus resources on core functionality</li>
                        <li>Provide instant updates without app store delays</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <p>We believe this shift will ultimately provide a better experience for all Harmony users with fewer technical issues and faster innovation.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        
